<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Karanis</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Διοσκόρῳ πραιποσίτῳ <num value="5">ε</num> πάγου 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>σιδώρου Πτολεμαίου ἀπὸ κώμης 

    <lb n="3"/>Καρανίδος τοῦ ὑπὸ σὲ πάγου. οἶδας μὲν καὶ αὐ-

    <lb n="4"/>τός, πραιποσίτων ἄριστε, πολλάκις τῶν 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>μειζόνων</corr><sic>μιζονων</sic></choice> <choice><corr>φοιτήσαντα</corr><sic>φυτησαντα</sic></choice> γράμματα εἴ που 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>φανείη</corr><sic>φανιη</sic></choice> ζῷα σπόρον <choice><corr>λυμαίνοντα</corr><sic>λυμενοντα</sic></choice> ταῦτα 

    <lb n="7"/>μὲν δημοσίᾳ πιπράσκεσθαι καὶ τὴν τιμὴν 

    <lb n="8"/>τῷ πολιτικῷ λόγῳ <choice><corr>χωρεῖν</corr><sic>χοριν</sic></choice>, τὸ δὲ ἀζή-

    <lb n="9"/>μιον τῶν παραπολομένων τῷ δεσπότῃ 

    <lb n="10"/>περισῴζεσθαι. <choice><corr>ἐπεὶ</corr><sic>επι</sic></choice> τοίνυν <choice><corr>κατέσπειρα</corr><sic>κατεσπιρα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="11"/>μετὰ π<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>λλῶν καμάτων μόνας ἀρούρας ἑπτὰ <num value="7"/> 

    <lb n="12"/>ἐν σίτῳ ἀπὸ ἀρουρῶν ὀγδοήκοντα <num value="80"/>, <choice><corr>ταύτας</corr><sic>ταυτα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="13"/>δὲ τέλειον κατεβρώθη ὑπὸ τετραπόδων, 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ τῆς παραστάσεως τῶν αἰτίων τοῖς δημο-

    <lb n="15"/>σίοις διαφερούσης, τάδε σοι τὰ ἔνγραφα ἐπιδίδω-

    <lb n="16"/>μι ὅπως τούτους μετακαλεσάμενος ἐπὶ σοῦ τὰ τοῖς 

    <lb n="17"/>νόμοι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> ἀκόλουθα πράξῃς ἵνα μὴ δι᾽ αὐτοὺς φυγῇ 

    <lb n="18"/>χρήσωμαι.      διευτύχει. 

    <lb n="19"/>τοῖς ἐσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>μένοις ὑπάτοις τὸ <num value="4">δ</num> Μεχὶρ <num value="4">δ</num>. 

    <lb n="20"/>Ἰσίδωρος ἐπιδέδωκα. Παῦλος ἔγραψα ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="21"/>ἀγραμμάτου. </ab></div><div n="meta.10409" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.10409" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" value="0324-01-30" notBefore="324" notAfter="324">30. Jan. 324</date></p></div><div n="meta.10409" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. CSBE, S. 109.</p></div><div n="meta.10409" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Isid.</title><biblScope type="numbers">78</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">10409</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0088</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">78</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0088;;78" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.10409" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.10409" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Karanis</placeName> (<geogName type="nome" cert="high" full="yes">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName type="ancientRegion" key="Aegyptus" cert="high" full="yes">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.10409" type="figure" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair.Isid.&amp;vVol=&amp;vNum=78"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>